
inform vim of cscope.out:
-------------------------
:cs add /path/to/cscope.out 

command prefixes:
-----------------
CTRL-\ # do command in current window
CTRL-SPACE # do command in new split window 
CTRL-SPACE CTRL-SPACE # do command 
CTRL-t # jump back to previous file

search methods:
---------------
s # usages
g # declaration 
f # header file 

final command:
--------------
# when hovering over a word
[command prefix][search method] 

Examples:
CTRL-\s # search for usages of word and jump to specified location in current window
